title: BATMAN ZERO YEAR DIRECTOR'S CUT 001 (2013) (Digital) (Zone-Empir
description:
I realize that mirrormaster82 already compiled this in his New 52 Week 100 torrent, but I expect someone who likes Batman will post a comment asking for it. He is the world's greatest detective - his fans, often, are not.  ;-)  And by the way, Zone messed up the file name but I only changed this post's title. --STF

BATMAN ZERO YEAR: THE DIRECTOR'S CUT #1

Reprinting the first chapter of this new story arc that begins in BATMAN #21 from the stunning pencil art of Greg Capullo and Rafael Albuquerque, with the full, action-packed scripts by Scott Snyder and James Tynion IV!

Written by: Scott Snyder
Art by: Greg Capullo
Backup Written by: Scott Snyder, James T Tynion IV
Backup Art by: Rafael Albuquerque
Cover by: Greg Capullo

Color, 64 Pages
On Sale: July 31, 2013
